/enum.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/decoder/DataClassDecoder.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/decoder/RegexDecoder.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/decoder/primitives.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/decoder/ListDecoder.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/decoder/PropsDecoder.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/decoder/Base64Decoder.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/decoder/ranges.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/decoder/MapDecoder.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/decoder/SecondsDecoder.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/decoder/SecretDecoder.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/decoder/pairs.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/decoder/urls.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/decoder/BigDecimalDecoder.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/decoder/LocaleDecoder.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/decoder/SealedClassDecoder.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/decoder/SortedSetDecoder.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/decoder/InlineClassDecoder.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/decoder/files.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/decoder/SetDecoder.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/decoder/SizeInBytesDecoder.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/decoder/InetAddressDecoder.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/decoder/MinutesDecoder.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/decoder/PrincipalDecoder.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/decoder/uuid.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/decoder/metric.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/decoder/Decoder.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/decoder/dates.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/decoder/KClassDecoder.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/Constants.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/time/\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/time/Durations.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/time/Period.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/ClasspathResourceLoader.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/transformer/\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/transformer/PathNormalizer.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/transformer/NodeTransformer.kt\ncom/sksamuel/hoplite/fp.kt\n--- docs?\n# Hoplite <img src=\"logo.png\" height=40>\n\nHoplite is a Kotlin library for loading configuration files into typesafe classes in a boilerplate-free way.\nDefine your config using Kotlin data classes, and at startup Hoplite will read from one or more config files,\nmapping the values in those files into your config classes. Any missing values,